# Final Reality Check

Is this solo-dev viable?

Yes — if:

* Physics stays approximation-based
* Temporal layer limited to 3–4 core mechanics at launch
* Visuals are stylized, not realistic

No — if:

* You attempt real rigid-body physics
* You attempt synchronous multiplayer
* You over-expand module count

